{"by":"uyzstvqs","id":47775836,"parent":47729327,"text":"Simplest auth UX that&#x27;s reasonably secure: Enter email, send link to email, click link.<p>Or you can use a phone number, call them, have them enter a numeric code. Just keep in mind that two people may use the same landline.<p>Or, tell them to write the password down and keep it somewhere safe. That usually works.","time":1776238728,"type":"comment"}